{"tid":1576601,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[又冇人知] 許智峰民事起訴警方非法拘捕和禁錮","createTime":"2019-09-17T10:12:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T13:31:08.000Z","uid":99478,"like":348,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":105,"replies":[{"pid":"cc26e82d703bde25b103424835d3001776182b70","tid":1576601,"uid":99478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T10:12:06.000Z","msg":"From: 立場<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B6%89%E9%98%BB%E5%B7%AE%E8%BE%A6%E5%85%AC%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%E5%BE%8C%E8%B8%A2%E4%BF%9D-%E8%A8%B1%E6%99%BA%E5%B3%B0%E8%BD%9F%E8%AD%A6%E6%BF%AB%E6%8D%95-%E6%9C%89%E8%AD%89%E6%93%9A%E6%AD%A1%E8%BF%8E%E6%8B%8E%E4%B8%8A%E6%B3%95%E5%BA%AD/?fbclid=IwAR0TBHCEZTheeqx0quMqz3nFpovNveED1kyUhsEdhSE5qpw6sbgilg07Cuo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B6%2589%25E9%2598%25BB%25E5%25B7%25AE%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E5%2585%25AC%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595%25E5%25BE%258C%25E8%25B8%25A2%25E4%25BF%259D-%25E8%25A8%25B1%25E6%2599%25BA%25E5%25B3%25B0%25E8%25BD%259F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BF%25AB%25E6%258D%2595-%25E6%259C%2589%25E8%25AD%2589%25E6%2593%259A%25E6%25AD%25A1%25E8%25BF%258E%25E6%258B%258E%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25BA%25AD%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0TBHCEZTheeqx0quMqz3nFpovNveED1kyUhsEdhSE5qpw6sbgilg07Cuo&d=ZtzEMfLxU%2BwdrFVc2rz1%2F0zlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=052bbf0d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B6%2589%25E9%2598%25BB%25E5%25B7%25AE%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E5%2585%25AC%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595%25E5%25BE%258C%25E8%25B8%25A2%25E4%25BF%259D-%25E8%25A8%25B1%25E6%2599%25BA%25E5%25B3%25B0%25E8%25BD%259F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BF%25AB%25E6%258D%2595-%25E6%259C%2589%25E8%25AD%2589%25E6%2593%259A%25E6%25AD%25A1%25E8%25BF%258E%25E6%258B%258E%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25BA%25AD%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0TBHCEZTheeqx0quMqz3nFpovNveED1kyUhsEdhSE5qpw6sbgilg07Cuo&h=e0dc1b04\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B6%89%E9%98%BB%E5%B7%AE%E8%BE%A6%E5%85%AC%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%E5%BE%8C%E8%B8%A2%E4%BF%9D-%E8%A8%B1%E6%99%BA%E5%B3%B0%E8%BD%9F%E8%AD%A6%E6%BF%AB%E6%8D%95-%E6%9C%89%E8%AD%89%E6%93%9A%E6%AD%A1%E8%BF%8E%E6%8B%8E%E4%B8%8A%E6%B3%95%E5%BA%AD/?fbclid=IwAR0TBHCEZTheeqx0quMqz3nFpovNveED1kyUhsEdhSE5qpw6sbgilg07Cuo</a><br />\n<br />\n星期日（9 月 15 日）晚在北角涉嫌阻差辦公被捕的民主黨立法會議員許智峰，他今日下午見記者，指自己被扣近 40 小時後「踢保」，無條件釋放。他認為反映警方根本無證據拘捕起訴他，「如果有證據，歡迎拎上法庭，俾公眾睇下你點非法濫捕」，他亦不相信警方有合理機會將他定罪。<br />\n<br />\n許智峰和律師商討後，在被拘留期間已指示律師入稟區域法院，要求法庭發出傳票，民事起訴警方非法拘捕和禁錮，答辯人包括警務處長、當日一名機動部隊警司和拘捕他的警員。"},{"pid":"e3312aa059e7ff623b08465d6066e38117964ff8","tid":1576601,"uid":33930,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T10:12:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yt2HG33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyt2HG33.jpg&h=9fcb0aae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TrPZKfU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTrPZKfU.jpg&h=433e1fe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【922攻略流出】<br />\n907<span style=\"color: gold;\">加強版</span>配合hkmap live <br />\n更「大局」交通測試，彩虹戰衣、影帝、機巴、塞鐵、嶄新突擊RB、私家車傾巢而出，裡應外合 <br />\n+機場員工集體Call Sick <br />\n+雷達站/機場附近新搞作<br />\n+大量中港貨櫃司機加入物資支援！<br />\n<br />\n更多攻略，陸續公布，敬請留意"},{"pid":"587ad5b44f8fb3b9c5979ec38b85bda7da997aa6","tid":1576601,"uid":108337,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T10:16:41.000Z","msg":"勇武派<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ed6b02277be58eb5a62f29796c34c726e56620a","tid":1576601,"uid":216417,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T10:17:55.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"0c482aba30dfda56fb865e6f08aae365660e9125","tid":1576601,"uid":58670,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T10:18:16.000Z","msg":"許智峰<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma